{"tid":2379101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良稱若提早封區效果更好，梁子超建議擴大強檢範圍，袁國勇今早視察麗港城感染情況","createTime":"2021-01-25T04:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T05:19:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2349fd3464dfa3f89e86e2301bef8d2c51f7846c","tid":2379101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572204-20210125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572204-20210125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=46b5414e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572204-20210125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b48ea82a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572204-20210125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，在區域內發現的陽性個案比例偏高，認為封區行動是有需要，但時機上做得比較慢，如果提早做，效果更好。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超認為，按確診個案分析，今次封區的行動，成本效益與普通的強檢一樣，未能發揮作用，建議擴大強檢範圍，已能截斷部分傳播鏈。"},{"pid":"49f5e2b443b1eacc0551918fc0bfd478861a1590","tid":2379101,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"3隻醫官禽獸"},{"pid":"5bb9ce70589cfc1cf1ce1dc5c10ffc6d019a1ad2","tid":2379101,"uid":117689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1eab20e413c6330278783e053f837a0f5942c6","tid":2379101,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"袁國勇 許樹昌 何栢良 梁卓偉 <br />\n<br />\n梁子超 張竹君 徐德義 陳勁松"},{"pid":"80669922b292c8bda109af7c955aef20f48a00e9","tid":2379101,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:22:08.000Z","msg":"幾時封太古城？"},{"pid":"d518dad0ca767fcf2013e7c38ba43c64ec6cb67f","tid":2379101,"uid":